        "subject": "=New Issue Logged: {{$json.issue_title}}\n\n",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.project_manager_firstname}} {{$json.project_manager_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>An issue has been logged in the system and assigned for review and resolution.</p>\n\n<p><b>Issue Details</b><br>\n* Issue Title: {{$json.issue_title}}<br>\n* Description: {{$json.description}}<br>\n* Issue Type: {{$json.issue_type}}<br>\n* Priority: {{$json.issue_priority}}<br>\n* Current Status: {{$json.issue_status}}<br>\n* Related Project ID: {{$json.project_id}}<br>\n* Linked Task ID: {{$json.task_management_id}}<br>\n* Created By: {{$json.created_by_firstname}} {{$json.created_by_lastname}}<br>\n* Created On: {{$json.created_at}}</p>\n\n<p>Please review the issue details and initiate corrective action as appropriate.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\n<b>Issue & Quality Management System</b></p>",
